Turn Undead
Discworld ritual help
Turn Undead

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Turn undead - Ritual to harm undead creatures with holy power.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is an offensive ritual for use against undead creatures, 
damaging them with the holy power of your god.  The amount
of damage the victim receives will depend on your skill in
performing offensive rituals, and the holy symbol of your
god will be needed to perfom it.
.EP
